Вакансія від 17 березня 2020
Customer Support Specialist
Netgame
IT;
50–250 співробітників
Київ
Неповна зайнятість.
Досвід роботи від 1 року.
Опис вакансії
Our team Customer Support Specialist with excellent English for products targeted on EU customers.Requirements:
high literacy level of speech and writing (Russian and English);
ability to work in intensive mode;
computer skills;
experience in related fields;
ability to work with large volumes of information and willingness to learn;
willingness to learn quickly;
high level of self-control;
Duties:
providing expert advice on the technical and financial parts of products using online chat;
sending requests to solve technical and financial difficulties of users and receiving feedback for the purpose of subsequent informing users;
informing about identified problems or errors on supported resources.
Working conditions:
work schedule: 12-hours work shifts, 2/2 (day&night);
comfortable office five minutes walk from metro Palace Ukraine;
working in a strong team on commercially successful products.
This is a great opportunity to get a stable job with the possibility of professional and career growth.If you meet the specified requirements — we are waiting for your CV.
